whole_object: This pub is so quiet, you can hear a pint drop!
single_object:
- Tables: These tables are outstanding in their field – especially since there's no field around.
- Chairs: These chairs are always supportive, even when you take their seats for granted.
- Television: The television is truly flat-out entertaining.
- Bar counter: This bar counter serves more spirits than a haunted mansion.
- Plants: These plants are so good at photosynthesis, they really know how to turn the lights on.
- Lights: These lights never get bright ideas; they're too busy illuminating others.
- Menu board: This menu board is where chalk outlines of today's specials are found – no crime scene, just fine cuisine!
- Bar stools: The bar stools are the best in 'supporting roles,' always under the limelight.
